  "text": "Given the many interlinked elements of invasion ecology, there is no single ideal structure for a broad review such as the one we attempt here. Each part of the story demands a link to several others. The headings below start with an emphasis on general and overarching aspects, and move through organism-focused to ecosystem-centred considerations. The terminology used in the paper (following [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] ) is outlined in Figure 1 .",
